    },
    {
      "_key": "cb1850b92a71",
      "_type": "speechBlock",
      "align": "left",
      "iconUrl": "https://mamasanmoney-bu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/cropped-IMG_69AD0D2F343E-1-2-300x300.jpeg",
      "name": "ひーち部長",
      "paras": [
        "エアコンの掃除は使わない時期に♪"
      ]
    },
    {
      "_key": "6682ce879586",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "73e451eff8dc",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "エアコンのあの独特なカビの匂い今年こそスッキリしたいですね。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "28791dc3e651",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "96d139782f4b",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "本格的なエアコン使用シーズンを迎える前に点検も兼ねて業者に依頼してみましょう。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "2a506f3b2e7d",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "9b0cd57115d4",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "ひーち部長の場合、現在の住居へ住み始めて10年目を迎え2022年はお家のメンテに気を配りました。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "d99e61f3a552",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "f7c23b45f6b1",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "というのも、これまで自分では手の届きにくい場所のお掃除は"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "1bbad7999037",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "ab7291f58108",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "ものぐさな性格なため見て見ぬふりをしておりました。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "be164c3635d3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "d804a1a7d8b3",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "一念発起して思い切って業者さんへ依頼することに！"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "8794c0443604",
      "_type": "speechBlock",
      "align": "right",
      "iconUrl": "https://mamasanmoney-bu.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/C204902D-B54F-43B3-B6DF-88B08C9AEBF6-e1668691519166.png",
      "name": "まるお部員",
      "paras": [
        "結局自分ではやらないんかーい！"
      ]
    },
    {
      "_key": "181c06d540f2",
      "_type": "speechBlock",
      "align": "left",
      "iconUrl": "https://mamasanmoney-bu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/cropped-IMG_69AD0D2F343E-1-2-300x300.jpeg",
      "name": "ひーち部長",
      "paras": [
        "だから、ものぐさなのよ。。。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "_key": "3d338edc31c5",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "099dc99531d9",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "そして結論から申し上げると・・・・"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "7f57f0fae1c8",
      "_type": "speechBlock",
      "align": "left",
      "iconUrl": "https://mamasanmoney-bu.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/cropped-IMG_69AD0D2F343E-1-2-300x300.jpeg",
      "name": "ひーち部長",
      "paras": [
        "やっぱりプロの仕上がりは素晴らしい✨"
      ]
    },
    {
      "_key": "f936cc934467",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "b22b2467a052",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "満足度が断然違いました。お金を払っただけのことはあります。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "92a6e0192277",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "be0ddfaf9143",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "この記事では実体験をもとに"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "_key": "4a8a24a642ce",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "990fc4d8ffc6",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "「エアコン分解洗浄」について費用とともにご紹介いたします。"
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [],
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
